<section id="happy">
  <title>Mallard makes writers happy</title>
  <list>
    <item><p>Easily assemble documents from topics. Reuse. Remix.
    Stop writing maps by hand.</p></item>

    <item><p>Write links once. Navigation links are automatically two-way.
    Users can find their way no matter which page is page one.</p></item>

    <item><p>Track the progress and status of each topic for multiple
    versions and deliverables.</p></item>

    <item><p>Single source with powerful <link xref="/about/learn/if">conditional
    processing</link> with branching.</p></item>
  </list>
</section>

